    so we use kfree_rcu() instead of the call_rcu(ipc_immediate_free).
    
    Signed-off-by: Lai Jiangshan <laijs@cn.fujitsu.com>
    Signed-off-by: Paul E. McKenney <paulmck@linux.vnet.ibm.com>
